{"tid":1531360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開學日未忘反送中  葵涌兩校學生互嗌口號","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:16:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63588b8e79a42b227f0e3ee9706f62bd32b5fe1a","tid":1531360,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190902/_2019090214102332939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190902%2F_2019090214102332939.jpg&h=48667117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新學年今日開始，有人發起今日罷課，有學生參與，表達對《逃犯條例》修訂以及警察濫用暴力的不滿。葵涌兩間相鄰中學的學生，疑在小息時互嗌口號，就近日社會紛爭發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n片段見到，葵涌的樂善堂顧超文中學的學生，與相鄰的順德聯誼總會李兆基中學學生，疑在小息時互嗌「光復香港，時代革命」、「五大訴求，缺一不可」的口號。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1581966/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%98%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E5%85%A9%E6%A0%A1%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%92%E5%97%8C%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5</code></pre>"},{"pid":"137f95c1cb204038a0e5e9f80dbeed32e13c6b44","tid":1531360,"uid":57044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"好想喊... 香港後生，中學生真係世界第一。勇敢，無懼"},{"pid":"c2fef163c5d5fcbec6f83cbf60689fbcee97119d","tid":1531360,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475c85957353c414b0483e7b4c16db6d09fab266","tid":1531360,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"香港既學生真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284f55ba304b22fce90db682f84af717d8690841","tid":1531360,"uid":76538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:55:21.000